					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287" rend="visible">
						<summary>The novellae of Yom Ṭov ben Ishbili on the tractate Bava metsi῾a.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="tmr-Hebr">Hebrew, Aramaic</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
							<locus from="1r" to="256v"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ḥidushim </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">חדושים </title>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/286424530">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/286424530" xml:lang="en">Yom Tov ben Abraham Ishbili, 1250-1330</persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/286424530" xml:lang="he">אשבילי, יום טוב בן אברהם </persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>Agrees with the excerpts contained in Asifat zekenim of Rabi Betsalel on the same tractate.</p>
								<p>Quotes several rabbinic authorities, including Ramban, Rashba, and Aharon ha-Levi.</p>
							</note>
							<colophon xml:lang="he">סליקא נה מסכת בבא מציעא להריטב"א ז"ל שנת <date when="1553" calendar="Hebrew">ישי"ג</date> את זרע: <name type="person" role="scribe">משה אגימאן</name> חזק:<locus n="256r"/>
